Title: CS674 Spring 1996 Course Materials
Body: The project proposal should contain a short description of: the topic/problem in which you're interested the papers that you'll read (if you're doing a "reading" project) a description of the general approach you plan to use to solve the problem (if you're doing a "programming" project) plan for evaluation of the theory/technique (for both types of project) What to Turn in for the Project Official due date: Friday 5/3.
